	   <tr><td colspan=2>LMAO,<br>Do not train 2HB.&nbsp;&nbsp;What are you nuts?<br>2Hb, is sweet agro management.  And with the right weapon, the damage output is so sweet(definately better than weilding two 1hb's, two piercers, or a combination of the two.  PLUS, you do not get the AGRO!!!<br><br>Our AC abilities are not designed to take agro.  I play a lvl 54 Vahshiir Beastlord on Cazic-Thule.  Keep all weapons skills maxed, it is easy enough to do.<br><br>Then when that ever so sweet Screamstaff, or Tarmok Battlestaff comes up, you can actually use it instead of wishing you had raised your skill.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
